name: Fresh Spring Rolls
author: Rayna Jordan
summary: These little veggie and shrimp filled wraps are a real hit at parties! Serve them with a spicy dipping sauce.
ingredients: 1 (6.5 ounce) can shrimp, rinsed and drained
⅓ cup sweet and sour sauce
directions: In a medium bowl, mix the cabbage, shrimp, sweet and sour sauce, celery and carrots
Fill a small bowl with hot water
Dip rice wrappers one at a time into the water
Allow wrappers to soften, then remove from the water and drain
As wrappers are removed from the water, fill each with 2 tablespoons of the cabbage mixture
Roll the wrappers and chill covered until serving
